admin-id.title: C++ Programming
admin-id.description: Master C++ in 60 days. Covers OOP, STL, algorithms, and building console projects.
admin-id.details:
Comprehensive C++ programming course designed to take you from beginner to advanced level in just 60 days.

• C++ fundamentals: syntax, variables, data types, operators, and basic I/O
• Object-Oriented Programming (OOP): classes, objects, constructors, destructors
• Inheritance: single, multiple, and multilevel inheritance concepts
• Polymorphism: function overloading, operator overloading, virtual functions
• Encapsulation and abstraction: access specifiers, data hiding
• Templates: function templates, class templates, and generic programming
• Exception handling: try-catch blocks, custom exceptions
• Standard Template Library (STL): containers, iterators, algorithms

Advanced C++ features:
• Smart pointers: unique_ptr, shared_ptr, weak_ptr
• Move semantics and perfect forwarding
• Lambda expressions and functional programming
• Modern C++ features (C++11, C++14, C++17, C++20)
• Multithreading: threads, mutexes, condition variables
• Memory management and RAII principles
• Design patterns implementation in C++
• File handling and stream operations

Practical projects:
• Build console applications and games
• Implement data structures and algorithms
• Create object-oriented applications
• Develop library management system, banking application
